reviewText:
The good:

-Original/Unique;
-Characters;
-Gameplay;
-Field of View of 90° (Modified via fov_desired #");
-Fitting Soundtrack;
-Rebindable Keys.
-Supports Subtitles.
-Achievements;
-Trading Cards;
-Steam Cloud;

The bad:

-Short 18 Chapters (Around 5-6 hours);
-Voice Acting;
-Character Animations;
-Linear;
-Repetitive;

Score: 7/10."
